snippet: A long-range strike from Ever Banega and two goals from fellow Argentine Mauro Icardi, all in the space of 11 minutes, gave Inter Milan a 3-0 win over Lazio and their third successive Serie A win on Wednesday....
lead_paragraph: A long-range strike from Ever Banega and two goals from fellow Argentine Mauro Icardi, all in the space of 11 minutes, gave Inter Milan a 3-0 win over Lazio and their third successive Serie A win on Wednesday.

headline.main: Two-Goal Icardi Gives Inter Third Successive Win
headline.print_headline: Two-Goal Icardi Gives Inter Third Successive Win
